➜河南诗人王琦伟：五绝·晨雾（外一首）
http://www.sohu.com/a/437880924_100115135	44333
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20201212/70b0b088ca0e40eb8eb8b8897ba0f9ca.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>五绝·晨雾（平水韵）</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>文/梦回桃花源（王琦伟）</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">大雾罩都城，朦胧梦幻生。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">人车还未见，早送笑谈声。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>2020·12·10</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20201212/a2f934c450e84ab998adec024900a70a.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong><span style="font-size: 16px;">﻿</span></strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>注:南阳古称南都</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>五绝·独玉湖（平水韵）</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>文/梦回桃花源（王琦伟）</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">冬景谁堪比，风骚独玉湖。</p>            <div class="lookall-box">
