➜江西诗人时差先生：臀
http://www.sohu.com/a/437881088_100115135	44497
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20201212/9b81a2135f58422eb3cd7fa6484866d1.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>臀</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>文/时差先生</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">草原 拱起嵴背</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">俨然一个睡美人</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">丰满圆润</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">曲线温柔 张弛弧度</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">山谷的风</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">绿了细小的腰肢</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">风情 把握山的弹性</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">臀线 宕开诗的朦胧</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">三分富阳</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">七分蕴光</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">勾勒出一个个曼妙身姿</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20201212/38edb4a793fd46808ba8788472f26309.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
