➜星连（广东）：徐州行之诗
http://www.sohu.com/a/437886947_100115135	51810
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20201212/c456be261b2f4ab49c40e1bdd4cc201e.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>五绝.徐州行（新韵）</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>文/星连</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">冬风一眼收，行迹在徐州。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">多少情和念，诗心永对流。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>2020.12.2</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20201212/e24482929a8a4d17846b70f9d6ef6df1.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>五绝.待梦（新韵）</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>文/星连</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">寻梦不知时，得来景入诗。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">村间无故路，欲问几人识。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>2020.12.3</strong></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
